    "After applying all the screening conditions for sample selection described in Sections 3.1 and 3.2, we get 57,078 MRS spectra, which belong to 10,441 stellar sources.",
    "This MRS time-domain sample of solar-like stars is employed for the following analysis.",
    "Table 1 gives the counts of the selected MRS spectra and stellar sources after each of the screening conditions for sample selection.",
    "The number in parentheses is the change in count relative to the previous step.",
    "The bottom row of Table 1 is also the counts of the final MRS time-domain sample of solar-like stars employed in this work after all the screening conditions."
